(53, 'Estrada do Sol', 'Tom Jobim', 'G', 120, '4/4', 'bonfa', 10, '\"Estrada do Sol\" (Road of the Sun) is a famous song by Brazilian bossa nova composer Antônio Carlos Jobim (music) and singer Dolores Duran (lyrics), which was first recorded in 1958. The cheerful piece is about leaving your worries behind to enjoy life in the sun. It has been covered by numerous artists.', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '[sbn_leadsheet title=\"Estrada do Sol\" composer=\"Tom Jobim\" key=\"G\" tempo=\"120\" time=\"4/4\" rhythm=\"bonfa\"]\n\n| Am7 D7       | Am7 D7       | Am7 Bm7      | Am7 Bm7      |\n| GMaj7 Am7    | Bm7 CMaj7    | GMaj7        | Cm7 F7(9)    |\n| Bm7 E7(9)    | Bbm7 Eb7(9)  |\n\n[sbn_voicings]\nAm7: x0201x\nBbm7: 6x666x @6\nBm7: x2023x\nCMaj7: x3x000\nCm7: 8x888x @8\nD7: x5453x @3\nE7(9): x7677x @6\nEb7(9): x6566x @5\nF7(9): x8788x @7\nGMaj7: 3x443x\n[/sbn_voicings]\n\n[sbn_info]\n[description]\n\"Estrada do Sol\" (Road of the Sun) is a famous song by Brazilian bossa nova composer Antônio Carlos Jobim (music) and singer Dolores Duran (lyrics), which was first recorded in 1958. The cheerful piece is about leaving your worries behind to enjoy life in the sun. It has been covered by numerous artists.\n[/description]\n[/sbn_info]\n\n[/sbn_leadsheet]', '{\"title\":\"Estrada do Sol\",\"composer\":\"Tom Jobim\",\"key\":\"G\",\"tempo\":120,\"timeSignature\":\"4/4\",\"measures\":[{\"chords\":[{\"name\":\"Am7\",\"beats\":2},{\"name\":\"D7\",\"beats\":2}]},{\"chords\":[{\"name\":\"Am7\",\"beats\":2},{\"name\":\"D7\",\"beats\":2}]},{\"chords\":[{\"name\":\"Am7\",\"beats\":2},{\"name\":\"Bm7\",\"beats\":2}]},{\"chords\":[{\"name\":\"Am7\",\"beats\":2},{\"name\":\"Bm7\",\"beats\":2}]},{\"chords\":[{\"name\":\"GMaj7\",\"beats\":2},{\"name\":\"Am7\",\"beats\":2}]},{\"chords\":[{\"name\":\"Bm7\",\"beats\":2},{\"name\":\"CMaj7\",\"beats\":2}]},{\"chords\":[{\"name\":\"GMaj7\",\"beats\":4}]},{\"chords\":[{\"name\":\"Cm7\",\"beats\":2},{\"name\":\"F7(9)\",\"beats\":2}]},{\"chords\":[{\"name\